Asset
    an item of property owned by a person or company, regarded as having value and available to meet debts, commitments, or legacies.

Commodity - Emtia
    a raw material or primary agricultural product that can be bought and sold, such as copper or coffee.
    grains, gold, beef, oil, and natural gas..
    
    Commodity Companies
        
        
Commodities are physical products that are meant to be consumed or used in the production process. 
Assets, on the other hand, are goods that are not consumed through their use.



# KDV Hesaplama
Hesaplama FormÃ¼lleri
SatÄ±ÅŸ TutarÄ±; KDV Dahil ise aÅŸaÄŸÄ±daki formÃ¼le uygun iÅŸlem gerÃ§ekleÅŸtiriniz.
Ã–rnek: % 1
  MÃ¼ÅŸterinizden 1000 tl  tahsil ettin. SattÄ±ÄŸÄ±nÄ±z mal/hizmet KDV oranÄ± %1 ise;
  
